body.name: ZOSI C296 Plug-in 4K 8MP Wired WiFi PT Security Camera Outdoor, Pan/Tilt Wireless Camera with AI Person Vehicle Face Detect, Starlight Color Night Vision, Siren Alert, 2-Way Talk (128GB SD Card)
deliveryMessages: Delivery Thursday, February 15. Order within 5 hrs 44 mins
features: (1). [ Get Smarter Alerts that Matter ] __ Elevate your security with the ZOSI C296 IP Camera's intelligent AI detection, targeting people, vehicles, pets, and packages. Say goodbye to false alarms from moving bugs or rustling leaves. Customize motion detection zones to receive only the most relevant notifications. When motion is detected, sound and light alarms activate automatically, and you receive prompt emails and push notifications directly to your mobile device.

(2). [ Stable Plug-in Power Supply & Auto Motion Tracking with Wider Coverage ] __ Improve security coverage with a wide 140-degree vertical and 355-degree horizontal rotation, eliminating blind spots. The camera intelligently tracks moving targets, providing plug-and-play convenience via a power adapter for seamless 24/7 recording—ensuring no missed significant moments. Note: Camera supports 5X digital zoom.

(3). [ 4K Super HD & Starlight Color Night Vision ] __ Experience superior image quality with the ZOSI C296 8MP 4K Super HD camera, featuring a high-sensitivity starlight sensor for exceptional low-light performance. Unlike traditional Wi-Fi cameras, it excels in low-light conditions. Equipped with 6 infrared lights and 4 warm lights, it offers 3 night vision modes: (A) Default infrared black & white night vision, (B) Full-color night vision, and (C) Auto (smart) night vision.

(4). [ Built to Last & Two Way Audio ] __ Rely on the IP66 weatherproof design and high-quality materials to withstand rainy or snowy days, extending the camera's lifecycle. The built-in speaker and microphone enable two-way audio functionality, allowing you to use preset or personalized voice messages to either deter or welcome visitors.

(5). [ Remote Control & 2 Storage Options ] __ Stay connected with the live stream via the free "ZOSI Smart" mobile app anytime, anywhere (compatible with 2.4GHz Wi-Fi, not 5GHz). Record videos to a Micro SD Card (included 128GB SD Card) or opt for unlimited cloud storage at a nominal fee in case of camera damage. Your security, your choices.
